{"tid":1916268,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥迪奧拿：想踢陣容齊整的曼聯，希望拉舒福特盡早康復","createTime":"2020-03-08T18:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T01:54:31.000Z","uid":204475,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6fac490a3349123f0721aa0a7944466b35775b0f","tid":1916268,"uid":204475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:31:35.000Z","msg":"哥迪奧拿在接受採訪時，談到了接下來的曼市打比，他表示自己更願意面對陣容齊整的曼聯。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;從我當上主教練的第一天起，我就想和各個完整陣容的球隊交手。我想在班拿貝對陣有夏薩特的皇馬，不希望和缺少拉舒福特的曼聯、失去卡尼的熱刺對抗。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我希望能和對手的所有頂級球員交手，但這對曼聯來說是不利的，他們有一部分傷員。我更願意踢有拉舒福特的曼聯，希望他能盡快康復。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;但曼聯依然還有別的頂級球員，我會考慮他們用馬迪爾、詹士還有費南迪斯，還有恩哈路。要預防的還有曼聯的比賽方式，他們近期用了三到四種不同的進攻體系。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb214788d3cc4a64adb4d53e15286c40ccf2eef","tid":1916268,"uid":12680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:32:24.000Z","msg":"需要盡快輸一場"},{"pid":"a515d784d3591d6c2000ea48180aed97d326aaea","tid":1916268,"uid":70691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:33:12.000Z","msg":"屌 佢次次講野都出事<br />\n'曼城需要盡快輸一場波'"},{"pid":"8b358d81c08f234fb821d597de2fe4c071fbfbb3","tid":1916268,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bb214788d3cc4a64adb4d53e15286c40ccf2eef","tid":1916268,"uid":12680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:32:24.000Z","msg":"需要盡快輸一場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"Bin到2046<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}